Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是牺牲了珍贵的饮水\N选择把它用在克劳地亚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊，先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.94,0:19:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2300…2280
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，你先上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个位子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来坐前座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.80,0:19:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红色先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到防空站去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有银之战舰的\N紧急避难防空站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要到那里\N就可以获得补给和维修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前方的弧形岩石为标的\N转到2点钟方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.71,0:20:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,标的在前方2点钟方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解，舵转2点方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.57,0:20:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.81,0:21:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩子！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.68,0:22:39.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
