Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.83,0:23:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回预告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.73,0:23:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，一路顺风哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
